40 ited to, child care, travel, meals, lodging and an amount equivalent to the worker’s net lost wages
41 for the period during which the worker is absent if the worker does not receive benefits pursuant
42 to ORS 656.210 (4) during the period of absence. A claim for “related services” described in this
43 paragraph shall be made in the manner prescribed by the director.
